Description: Hequation Review is a monthly economic policy and research publication series published by Hequation, an independent economic policy and research organisation based in Lagos, Nigeria. The Review publishes rigorous, evidence-based commentary and analysis on African economic policy, digital finance, financial inclusion, energy economics, FinTech, and development economics.
URL: https://repec.hequation.com/
